originalText.text: A mental health, ketamine psychedelic psychotherapist  expert!! Great website, marketing,  nothing spared. video's galore.  Jetting around the world preaching solutions while on stage with Gabor Mate and Deepak Chopra, BUT was so flaky and NON helpful, even confused when my wife desperately tried to work with her.  She was able to send invoices in the thousands of dollars though.   What's her goal?  Turn away a Mom in need for the spotlight?

originalText.text:
I was VERY over-medicated under her care to the point of numbness. At one point, I was on 5 different medications for my anxiety and depression, including Ativan 4x day. She hands out meds like candy. This is not just my opinion -- every mental health-care provider I've spoken to since then have been shocked at the cocktail I was on.

She is also impossibly difficult to get a hold of, even in an emergency. I was admitted to the ER at one point and none of the doctors there could get in touch with her the entire day I was there. She never followed up on me after. My therapist also tried calling and emailing her several times to schedule a time to consult with her over my care, and couldn't get in touch with her.

I could not have made a better decision for my mental health and overall wellbeing when I switched psychiatrists.
